{
  "stem": "22463.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am not doing this for myself, at this time, all the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I give him a [INAUDIBLE] as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next day, when I was-- I having dinner, we had been sitting, the whole family, my mother, my wife, my sister, and the brothers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I bring the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sure that everybody was OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started to cut the bread, and I feed-- finished the two two kilos of bread but I was still hungry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in my mind, more than in my stomach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew about it a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Still, it was the Polish people who were coming from Krakow with these-- some messages, or something of this kind.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only a few of them had been.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had been late, they took part of the machinery, the very light one, out of the platforms and moved to the factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't move farther because there was still the textile machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was missing, they had to put it-- and also, it was quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little, exactly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Krakow, we have even more than in Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Schindler has a a very expensive cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He has a BMW.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has an Alfa Romeo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He has a Hudson, American model, with electric wheels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he has a German-- very expensive car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It looked like a Rolls Royce, but he has a powerful radio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they have been listening to the radio, or that, we have-- as much as-- as everybody else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you about the mood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had been losing 2 2 kilos a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're want to find out who was losing-- who was stealing some bread and potato. 2 kilos a week, we were losing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were running to the toilet all the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
